@base = http://localhost:8000/api

### Score history — last 30 days (default)
GET {{base}}/analytics/score-history

### Score history — last 7 days
GET {{base}}/analytics/score-history?days=7

### Score history — last 90 days
GET {{base}}/analytics/score-history?days=90

### Score history — last year
GET {{base}}/analytics/score-history?days=365

### Year in Pixels — current year
GET {{base}}/analytics/heatmap

### Year in Pixels — specific year
GET {{base}}/analytics/heatmap?year=2025

### Weekly summary — current week
GET {{base}}/analytics/weekly-summary

### Weekly summary — specific week
GET {{base}}/analytics/weekly-summary?week=2026-W14

### Category breakdown — last 30 days (default)
GET {{base}}/analytics/category-breakdown

### Category breakdown — custom range
GET {{base}}/analytics/category-breakdown?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-03-31

### Score correlations — last 30 days (default)
GET {{base}}/analytics/correlations

### Score correlations — last 90 days
GET {{base}}/analytics/correlations?days=90
